{
  "stem": "19111.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the mothers started screaming and yelling, and some of the mothers were begging the Nazis to allow them to escort their children.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "A few are allowed, and some were beaten over their head with-- with the rifle butts turned-- put aside.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was also pushed onto a truck, but there were also some elderly people in wheelchairs at the same time, too, that had to come with the children for this inoculation, supposedly.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And one German, a Gestapo guy, looks at me, and he says, you!",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He says, get off the truck and go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You, and you, and another kid, he says, you go and carry the old people, the invalids, in their wheelchairs, and put them on the truck.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so we had to jump off the truck, and go and carry those people, load them onto the trucks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And when all the trucks were loaded up, and everybody was gone, they sent some of the mothers back to the camp, and they kept us yet a little bit longer.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then they made a decision.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He says, you two, you're strong and you can still work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he said, you go back to the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was me and the other kid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Katz-- ?] was-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Shlomo Katz, ?] something like that, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my best friend was in this action.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "His name was Boria Trahtenberg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he wound up with this transport, and they took all these children to the train, loaded them onto a boxcar, and they all were taken to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remained with my-- with the other kid, and both of us were returned to the camp, just the two out of the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About 250 maybe 220.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
